meta {
  name: 04 Chat (SSE, LLM, guarded)
  seq: 4
}

docs {
  A runnable MULTI-TURN agent workflow over one persisted conversation:
  01 opens it, 02 follows up with a pronoun that only resolves against
  turn 1 ("Is *that* above the threshold…"), 03 provokes the tool-use
  loop (tool_use / tool_result events stream live; done lists
  tools_used), 04 replays the whole six-message thread for free. The
  three POSTs spend real (budget-guarded) LLM money and answer as
  Server-Sent-Events streams. Run in seq order — request 01 captures the
  conversation_id the rest of the folder reuses.
}
